ke mistakes. As PVR Narasimha Sir has often told one example about a loving=
 child towards father, and a smart child filing court case against father, =
I hope you remember it. So I feel devotion to Ambaa like an innocent child =
is more important than getting entangled in beeja mantras and making mistak=
es and getting punished for that.

3.       I feel the Bhavaani Ashtakam by=
 ShrimachShankara Bhagawathpujyapaatha Virachitha is the best. 

 

Naa Jaa=
naami Mantram, Naa Jaanaami Tantram, 

Gatistvam Gatistvam Tvamekaa Bhavaan=
i

 

