(meaning one whose speech is like ruby). He says that to worship Shiva one =
needs a wisdom which will be given by Shivaa Himself.(Avan Arulaaaley Avan =
thaal vanangi). In other words, I personally feel that we are not even qual=
ified to worship Divine Mother, because even for that worship we need some =
wisdom and methods of paaraayanam or pooja vidhaana.

5.       I simply cry=
 to Ambaa and express my inability to worship Her because of my Moodha-Math=
i polluted and weakened by Kali-Yuga and absence of guidance from Aachaarya=
